description: Vincent Reffet was part of the Jetman Dubai team, and performed airborne stunts around the world.
title: Vincent Reffet: French 'Jetman' dies in training accident
title_page: Vincent Reffet: French 'Jetman' dies in training accident - BBC News
maintext: "Vince was a talented athlete, and a much-loved and respected member of our team," the statement said. "Our thoughts and prayers are with his family and all those who knew and worked with him."
